    <Paragraph Margin="0,24,0,16" TextAlignment="Center" FontFamily="times new roman" FontWeight="Normal" FontSize="21">
      <Run Tag="__21">WHO HAD A BETTER YEAR,</Run>
      <LineBreak/>
      <Run Tag="__21">NOMAR GARCIAPARRA OR ICHIRO SUZUKI?</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Margin="0,16,0,24" TextAlignment="Center" FontFamily="times new roman" FontWeight="Normal" FontSize="19">
      <Run Tag="xhtml/part01chapter02.html#part01chapter02section01">The Runs-Created Approach</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Margin="0,1,0,0" TextAlignment="Justify" FontFamily="times new roman" FontSize="14">
      <Run FontFamily="times new roman" FontWeight="Normal" FontSize="40" Tag="__21">I</Run>
      <Run Tag="__21">n 2004 Seattle Mariner outfielder Ichiro Suzuki set the major league record for most hits in a season. In 1997 Boston Red Sox shortstop Nomar Garciaparra had what was considered a good (but not great) year. Their key statistics are presented in </Run>
      <Hyperlink NavigateUri="xhtml/part01chapter02.html#chapter02table01">
        <Hyperlink.TextDecorations>
          <TextDecorationCollection/>
        </Hyperlink.TextDecorations>
        <Run Tag="__21">table 2.1</Run>
      </Hyperlink>
      <Run Tag="__21">. (For the sake of simplicity, henceforth Suzuki will be referred to as &#x201C;Ichiro&#x201D; or &#x201C;Ichiro 2004&#x201D; and Garciaparra will be referred to as &#x201C;Nomar&#x201D; or &#x201C;Nomar 1997.&#x201D;)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph TextIndent="16" Margin="0,0,0,0" TextAlignment="Justify" FontFamily="times new roman" FontSize="14">
      <Run Tag="__21">Recall that a batter&#x2019;s slugging percentage is Total Bases (TB)/At Bats (AB) where</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Margin="0,1,0,0" TextAlignment="Justify" FontFamily="times new roman" FontSize="14">
      <Run Tag="__21">&#xA0;</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Table Tag="__21">
      <Table.Columns>
        <TableColumn Width="30.0177619893428*"/>
        <TableColumn Width="4.97335701598579*"/>
        <TableColumn Width="36.9449378330373*"/>
        <TableColumn Width="28.0639431616341*"/>
      </Table.Columns>
      <TableRowGroup>
        <TableRow FontSize="13">
          <TableCell TextAlignment="Left" FontSize="13">
            <Paragraph Margin="0,1,0,0" TextAlignment="Justify" FontFamily="times new roman" FontSize="11">
              <Run Tag="__21">&#xA0;</Run>
            </Paragraph>
          </TableCell>
          <TableCell TextAlignment="Left" FontSize="13">
            <Paragraph Margin="0,1,0,0" TextAlignment="Justify" FontFamily="times new roman" FontSize="11">
              <Run Tag="__21">TB =</Run>
            </Paragraph>
          </TableCell>
          <TableCell TextAlignment="Left" FontSize="13">
            <Paragraph Margin="0,1,0,0" TextAlignment="Justify" FontFamily="times new roman" FontSize="11">
              <Run Tag="__21">Singles + 2 &#xD7; Doubles (2B) + 3 &#xD7; Triples (3B)</Run>
              <LineBreak/>
              <Run Tag="__21">+ 4 &#xD7; Home Runs (HR).</Run>
            </Paragraph>
          </TableCell>
